Debug stub: Make HLT produce the same signal on Windows and Linux

Before this change, the debug stub reported SIGILL on Windows for the
x86 HLT instruction.

Change the Windows behaviour to match the Linux behaviour, which is to
produce SIGSEGV.

Change the debug stub test to check for exact signal numbers.

